Constructor & Destructor Documentation

EventConfig::EventConfig (  ) 

it is better to leave this one out as

This is a persistent class.

It contains virtually all information about a single measurement.

Default constructor. We have to allocate memory for fMeasInfo and fAnaInfo as they can be read from a file with a streamer. The streamers do not allocate memory by themselves.
